context.content:
Create a minemap with 'PlantUML' code with color, only output code and Traditional Chinese. Please make more details. The more details, the better. The higher the priority, the brighter the color.

Allow colors: white, application, aliceBlue, AntiqueWhite, aquarmarine, business, cora, whiteSmoke, yellow, orange, lightgrey, lightblue, lightgreen, lightpink, lightsalmon, lightskyblue, lightcyan,  lavender, lavenderblush, lemonchiffon, yellowGreen, greenYellow, Beige, Bisque, GhostWhite, technology, saeshell, strayrgy, pink, plum, palegoldenrod, tan, tomato.

Color must be in `[#color]` tag.

Example:

```
@startmindmap
+[#white] <&home> Right site
++[#color] <&aperture> AI Technologies
+++[#color] <&puzzle-piece> Machine Learning
++++[#color] <&tag> Supervised Learning
+++++[#color] <&code> Regression
++++++[#color] <&code> Regression
@endmindmap
```
